<html>

  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1>
      We wanted to thank you!
    </h1>

    <p>
      We cannot thank you enough for the time you took to provide us with your invaluable feedback!  Below you will find an exact copy of the email we just received.  If you have any questions, comments or concerns about this email or the one generated by the website, please do not hesitate to call <a href="tel:+14129214247">412-921-4247</a> or <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=244 Crafton Ingram Shopping Center, Pittsburgh, PA, 15205">stop by</a>.
    </p>
    <p>
      Thank you again and we look forward to helping expose your inner beauty in the future!
    </p>
    <p>
      Please note: Your email address was <strong>NOT</strong> stored in any database.  We protect your privacy by not storing anything.
    </p>

    <p>
      Our email:
    </p>
    <table>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th colspan="2"><h3>Customer Contact</h3></th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Name:</strong></td>
          <td><%= @body[:guest_name] %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Email:</strong></td>
          <td>
            <a href="mailto:<%= @body[:guest_email] %>" target="_blank"><%= @body[:guest_email] %></a>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Date:</strong></td>
          <td><%= @body[:request_date] %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2"><strong>Subject:</strong></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2"><%= @body[:guest_message_subject] %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2"><strong>Message:</strong></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td colspan="2"><%= @body[:guest_message] %></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
